The '''Feast of Lanterns''' was an annual week-long festival held in [[Shou Lung]] and [[Kozakura]] and celebrated in the city of [[Neverwinter]] on the [[Sword Coast North]] as of the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]]. It took place in the month of [[Tsou]] of the [[Kara-Turan calendar]] during the first new moon of the calendar year.

{{Quote|Ax, yes, the [[ox]]. Perhaps you have heard the phrase-"Year of the Ox?" Many millennia ago, our ancestors chose an animal by which to remember each of the twelve branches. So enamored were the layfolk with this memory device that, over the centuries, images of the animals worked their way into the celebration.|Envoy [[Taishi Fei]]}}
